name: Rockers Screen Printed Canvas Tote Bag
description:
This is a limited edition, hand pulled, screen printed canvas tote bag.

Printed in fabric ink, the image is of an old school rock 'n' roller making sure his quiff is in perfect shape! This is a hand drawn, one of a kind illustration created by Paper Shakers and will not be seen anywhere else out there.

The bag meaures 42 x 38 cm (16.50 x 15 in) and is made from 100% cotton.

It has been printed in fabric ink and cured so that it can be washed at 40° or cooler without any fading or colour bleeding.

A personalised thank you note included included with every purchase.

The bag is posted in a sturdy padded envelope so it gets to you safely!

name: Six - A Screen Printed Book of Space
description:
'Six' is a limited edition, 4 colour hand pulled screen printed book.

It has 16 pages and is made up from a broad range of designs and ideas responding to the word 'Space'.

It is A5 - 21 x 14.8 cm (8.3 x 5.8 in)

It is a limited edition of 30.

Each book is editioned and signed with a personalised thank you note included.

A FREE badge is included with each book.

The books are posted in sturdy padded envelopes.

name: Destruction of a Delinquent Screen Printed T Shirt
description:
This is a limited edition, hand screen printed T-Shirt.

Printed in fabric ink on 100% cotton Gildan shirts, this is a bold, graphic image of a young Elvis Presley and his screaming fans.

These T-Shirts are currently available in Medium size only which measures 78 x 52 cm (31 x 20.50 in) and are suitable for both men and women (see photos).

It has been printed in fabric ink and cured so that it can be washed at 40° or cooler without any fading or colour bleeding.

A personalised thank you note included included with every purchase.

The T-Shirts are posted in a sturdy padded envelope so it gets to you safely!

name: Diamond Jubilee crown screen print
description:
This is a 3 colour, hand pulled screen print, based on the Queen's coronation crown design.

Printed in Union Jack colours, the body of the crown is made up from African fabric patterns giving it a modern twist.

A2 size - 59.4 x 42 cm (23.4 x 16.5 in)

Edition of 30

Each print is signed and editioned and a personalised thank you note included.

The print is posted in a sturdy cardboard tube.
